<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ʿyny tftḥ kl ywm</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ʿyny tftḥ kl ywm lmạ bṣḥy wqbl ạlnwm
 tʿtny by kl ywm dạ ạnt rby kẖạlq ạlkwn
 ạlqrạr - mʿạk ạnạ bạmsẖy fy kl lḥẓẗ .. byk ạnạ bạfrḥ kl tẖạnyẗ
 bạsbḥ lyk .. ʿsẖạn ạnt .. ạ̹lhy ạlly fạdytny
 2- lyk yạrb bạ̉qdm qlby wạ̉fkạry wkl ḥyạty
 bạ̉rfʿ ạ̹ydy ạsbḥ ạsmk ạ̉sjd lyk wạhdy lk dẖạty
 3- lyk slṭạn ʿly kl ḥyạty wfy ạ̹ydk kl ạ̉wqạty
 mạsẖy wrạk wạnạ wạtẖq ạ̹nk trʿạny fy kl kẖṭwạty</lyrics>
<author>brsys fkry̱, rwbrt rfʿt</author>
